8d16ddf9-1c29-4441-a418-976177d42d63.title: Remsai
8d16ddf9-1c29-4441-a418-976177d42d63.text: Well done, well done. Not many find their way in here.

9b9780ca-3d83-469a-b414-381d7f33b387.title: Remsai
9b9780ca-3d83-469a-b414-381d7f33b387.text:
I'm Remsai, a tree gnome. We live in this maze for our
protection. Have a look around and enjoy.

62a03295-e269-4c70-88bd-fb80aa8ffbd4.title: Remsai
62a03295-e269-4c70-88bd-fb80aa8ffbd4.text:
The orb, they have the orb. It must be returned or
we're doomed.

83533a94-df4f-488d-96d8-ffe5c76dac01.title: Remsai
83533a94-df4f-488d-96d8-ffe5c76dac01.text: Hello, did you find the orb?

02f7eff3-ef3d-40b9-af23-fc56dd33d38b.title: Remsai
02f7eff3-ef3d-40b9-af23-fc56dd33d38b.text: Please, we must have the orb if we are to survive.

68646382-ef03-4547-b9ff-acd322f623d5.title: Remsai
68646382-ef03-4547-b9ff-acd322f623d5.text:
Khazard's men came. Without the orb we were
defenceless. They killed many and then took our last
hope, the other orbs.

d381d4f5-fbf6-4303-98d1-112b3f900b1b.title: Remsai
d381d4f5-fbf6-4303-98d1-112b3f900b1b.text:
Now surely we're all doomed. Without them the spirit
tree is useless.

81572ce8-b232-44f2-a1d3-d554e1bbc5d5.title: Remsai
81572ce8-b232-44f2-a1d3-d554e1bbc5d5.text:
You're back, well done brave adventurer. Now the orbs
are safe we can perform the ritual for the spirit tree.
We can live in peace once again.

c269244d-ad13-4028-b355-a7af466798b9.title: Remsai
c269244d-ad13-4028-b355-a7af466798b9.text: Hi there traveller.  You're a legend around these parts.
